      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="X32-07G1"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">By Dr S<hi rend="SMALL-CAPS">HERIDAN</hi>.</l></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-line-1"><hi rend="display-initial">D</hi>Ear Dean, since you in sleepy wise</l><l/><l n="2" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-line-2">Have op'd your mouth, and clos'd your eyes,</l><l/><l n="3" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-line-3">Like ghost I glide along your floor,</l><l/><l n="4" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-line-4">And softly shut the parlour-door;</l><l/><l n="5" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-line-5">For should I break your sweet repose,</l><l/><l n="6" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-line-6">Who knows what money you might lose?</l><l/><l n="7" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-line-7">Since oftentimes it has been found,</l><l/><l n="8" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-line-8">A dream has giv'n ten thousand pound.</l><l/><l n="9" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-line-9">Then sleep, my friend, dear Dean, sleep on,</l><l/><l n="10" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-line-10">And all you get shall be your own.</l><l/><l n="11" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-line-11">Provided you to this agree,</l><l/><l n="12" xml:id="spp-X32-07G1-line-12">That all you lose belongs to me.</l><l/><l/></lg></div>
      </div>
    </body>
